Data Preprocessing¶

In [4]:
# adding car age column and to drop unnecessary columns in dataframe
df=pd.read_csv("CarUsedPrices.csv")
df["Current Year"]=2024
df["Car Age"]=df["Current Year"]-df["Year"]
df.drop(["Current Year","Year","Name","Location"],axis=1,inplace=True)
df["Mileage"]=df["Mileage"].str.replace("kmpl","").str.replace("km/kg","").astype(float)
df["Engine"]=df["Engine"].str.replace("CC","").astype(float)
df["Power"]=df["Power"].str.replace("bhp","")
df.head()
